Tell HN: Interesting plugin for people opening thousands of tabs
text:
For a few months, maybe even a year now, I've been using a firefox plugin called "Tab Manager Plus for Firefox" [0] it's probably the only plugin where I can mass close all the tabs by name.

E.g. I want to close all googla.com tabs, so I type "google" and it closes for me. Of course, you can also right-click on which tab you want to close.

This plugin is very overlooked, but well worth it for people like me who open thousands of tabs.

[0] https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/tab-manager-plus-for-firefox/
